Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.ui.pane.plot

Class Summary
AbstractObservationPlotPane<T extends ObservationPlotModel> This class is the base class for chart panes containing a plot of a set of valid observations.
NewPhasePlotButtonPane This class represents a widget containing a button that when pressed will result in a new phase plot for the current dataset being generated after suitable parameter entry via a dialog.
ObservationAndMeanPlotPane This class represents a chart pane containing a plot for a set of valid observations along with mean-based data.
ObservationPlotPane This class represents a chart pane containing a raw plot for a set of valid observations (magnitude vs Julian Day).
PhaseAndMeanPlotPane This class represents a chart pane containing a phase plot for a set of valid observations along with mean-based data.
PhasePlotPane This class represents a chart pane containing a phase plot for a set of valid observations (magnitude vs standard phase).
TimeElementsInBinSettingPane This component permits the time-elements-in-bin value to be changed which in turn can be used to modify the means series in an observations and means plot.
VStarPlotDataRenderer This is VStar's plot data-point renderer.
